OL,6,FA recycling centre in Bristol remains
OL,7,Fclosed after an accidental fire broke
OL,8,Fout.
OL,10,FAvon Fire and Rescue Service was
OL,11,Fcalled to the Hartcliffe Way centre in
OL,12,FKnowle just after 9:30am on Friday 22
OL,13,FMarch.
OL,15,FThe blaze was contained to one of the
OL,16,Frecycling bays and extinguished by
OL,17,Ffour firefighters wearing breathing
OL,18,Fapparatus.
