OL,6,FFollowing the incident, Avon Fire and
OL,7,FRescue Service said: "Two fire engines
OL,8,Ffrom Bedminster were in attendance.
OL,10,F"The cause of the fire is thought to
OL,11,Fbe accidental ignition."
