OL,3,CBattery disposal warning issued after
OL,4,Cfire shuts recycling centre
OL,6,FIt said: "Our Hartcliffe Way reuse and
OL,7,Frecycling centre is currently closed
OL,8,Fto the public after a fire in one of
OL,9,Fthe recycling containers just after
OL,10,F9:30 this morning.
OL,12,F"The fire was contained to one of the
OL,13,Frecycling bays and fire crews,
OL,14,Fattending the scene quickly, were able
OL,15,Fto extinguish it.
OL,17,F"Our teams followed established
OL,18,Femergency procedures, and there were
OL,19,Fno injuries. We are grateful also for
OL,20,Fthe quick response by the fire service.
