OL,3,CBattery disposal warning issued after
OL,4,Cfire shuts recycling centre
OL,6,F"This incident highlights just how
OL,7,Fimportant is it to correctly dispose
OL,8,Fof potentially hazardous materials and
OL,9,Fitems containing batteries.
OL,11,F"Always: remove batteries from small
OL,12,Felectronics such as vapes, electric
OL,13,Ftoothbrushes and toys.
OL,15,F"Never: put batteries in with
OL,16,Fincorrect recycling (including metal
OL,17,Fand cans) or general waste, including
OL,18,Fyour outdoor wheelie bin."
