OL,6,FThe site is currently being monitored
OL,7,Fand Bristol Waste Company has said it
OL,8,Fwill provide an update when the
OL,9,Frecycling centre reopens to the public.
OL,11,FIn the meantime the Avonmouth reuse
OL,12,Fand recycling centre is open as usual
OL,13,Fand will be accepting visitors who had
OL,14,Fbooked a visit to Hartcliffe Way.
